This paper involves measuring the performance of an artificial intelligence system on a verbal IQ test, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of natural language processing tools and Python programming suggests a focus on computational linguistics (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). The spectral methods used in question answering may also relate to computational complexity (cs.CC). Finally, the study of AI systems and their abilities could fall under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
